flowchart TD
  A[Request] --> B{Route type?}
  B -- Planning / Notes --> C[Cache First]
  C --> D{Cache hit?}
  D -- Yes --> E[Serve from cache]
  D -- No --> F[Fetch network]
  F --> G[Update cache (TTL 24h)]
  B -- Auth / Mutations --> H[Network Only]
  B -- Static assets --> I[Stale While Revalidate]
  B -- Other pages --> J[Network First]
